    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction à PyCairo for Python2 Module</title>

      <para>
        Cette version de PyCairo fournit des liaisons
<application>Python2</application> à <application>Cairo</application>.
      </para>

      <!-- Does not use gcc -->
&lfs111_checked;
      

